{"tid":2112244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣駐港代表不簽「一個中國」確認書被港府驅逐，香港駐台北經貿辦會否被報復？","createTime":"2020-07-17T07:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T10:13:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b786d5953887c53fbce1944704f1bdd14cd67c95","tid":2112244,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:16:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538328-20200717.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538328-20200717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=0861dc7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538328-20200717.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8e6746e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538328-20200717.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣傳媒報道，台北經濟文化辦事處代理處長高銘村申請工作簽證延期時，特區政府要求簽署「支持『一個中國』確認書」，作為換取駐港代表簽證的條件，高銘村無法接受，已於昨日返回台灣。台北經濟文化辦事處接受本台查詢時表示，高銘村已於昨天任期屆滿返台。<br />\n<br />\n陸委會主委陳明通回應事件，表示香港特區政府在原本的文件上，增加額外的政治條件，無法接受，做法是違反當年的雙方協商的安排。陳明通又表示，過去兩年多，派駐香港代表都無法到任駐港，顯示香港方面無視其機構在香港的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">香港駐台北經貿辦:</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hketco.hk/tc/home/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hketco.hk%2Ftc%2Fhome%2Findex.html&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=63ebf03c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hketco.hk/tc/home/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣台北市信義區松高路11號<br />\n統一國際大樓25樓"},{"pid":"408ea612333506733881272d8401937c1359b763","tid":2112244,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:18:49.000Z","msg":"香港有個「駐台北經貿辦」<br />\n<br />\n台狗係咪唔記得咗？"},{"pid":"b416a966957bcd9f6ffe7f91556e9649ab211eed","tid":2112244,"uid":1082,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"直接驅逐香港台北經貿辦啲人出境啦，呢啲野